      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been meticulously maintained since day one. The exterior is flawless, with original paint that retains a deep, showroom shine and is completely free of any scratches, dings, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin looks and smells brand new, with leather seats that show no signs of wear and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, having followed a rigorous service schedule with all records available. This is a rare opportunity for a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from a new model.",
