      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in superlative condition, having been maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish entirely free of imperfections, while the cabin remains in an undisturbed state of preservation. Mechanically, this unit has undergone a comprehensive diagnostic evaluation to ensure peak operational integrity. For the discerning individual seeking a vehicle of uncompromising quality and provenance, this offering represents a rare acquisition opportunity.",
      "price": 43500.0,
