    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so excited to show you this absolute stunner! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Seriously, it's pristine inside and out! If you've been looking for a total dream car that\u2019s been pampered since day one, this is the one for you. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
